  "prompt": "What are some small restaurant chains in Dallas? (under 10 locations)",
  "response": "As of October 2023, Dallas boasts a variety of small restaurant chains that offer unique dining experiences while maintaining a regional presence with fewer than 10 locations. Here are some notable examples:\n\n1. **Mastretta Caf\u00e9 & Bakery**\n   - **Cuisine:** Mexican-inspired pastries and coffee\n   - **Description:** Known for its authentic Mexican baked goods, artisanal coffee, and cozy atmosphere, Mastretta has become a favorite spot for locals seeking quality pastries and a comfortable place to relax or work.\n   - **Locations:** 3\n\n2. **Cane Rosso Pizza**\n   - **Cuisine:** Neapolitan-style pizza\n   - **Description:** Specializing in authentic Neapolitan pizzas with fresh, high-quality ingredients, Cane Rosso offers a menu that emphasizes traditional flavors and artisanal craftsmanship.\n   - **Locations:** 6\n\n3. **Trust Pizza + Wine**\n   - **Cuisine:** Gourmet pizza and wine\n   - **Description:** Combining delicious, handcrafted pizzas with a curated selection of wines, Trust Pizza + Wine provides a sophisticated yet casual dining experience perfect for date nights or gatherings.\n   - **Locations:** 5\n\n4. **Two Sons Tavern**\n   - **Cuisine:** American comfort food\n   - **Description:** Offering a menu of classic American dishes with a modern twist, Two Sons Tavern focuses on creating a welcoming environment with hearty meals and a wide selection of beverages.\n   - **Locations:** 4\n\n5. **Legal Limit**\n   - **Cuisine:** Tex-Mex and Southwestern\n   - **Description:** Legal Limit serves up flavorful Tex-Mex and Southwestern cuisine in a vibrant setting, featuring signature dishes like their famous enchiladas and innovative margaritas.\n   - **Locations:** 7\n\n6. **Urban Crust Pizza House**\n   - **Cuisine:** Artisan pizza\n   - **Description:** Urban Crust Pizza House is known for its creative pizza toppings, fresh ingredients, and stylish interiors, making it a popular choice for pizza enthusiasts looking for something beyond the ordinary.\n   - **Locations:** 3\n\n7. **Velvet Taco**\n   - **Cuisine:** Gourmet tacos\n   - **Description:** Velvet Taco offers an eclectic menu of gourmet tacos with diverse and inventive fillings, appealing to foodies looking for unique and flavorful options.\n   - **Locations:** 8\n\n8. **Social Craft Wine Bar**\n   - **Cuisine:** Wine and small plates\n   - **Description:** A sophisticated spot for wine lovers, Social Craft Wine Bar pairs a vast selection of wines with thoughtfully prepared small plates, ideal for wine tastings and intimate gatherings.\n   - **Locations:** 2\n\nThese small chains contribute to Dallas's vibrant and diverse culinary scene, offering residents and visitors a variety of dining options beyond the large, national franchises. If you're interested in visiting any of these restaurants, I recommend checking their official websites or contacting them directly for the most up-to-date information on locations and operating hours.",
